trailingComments.value: * Transform the provided value into a boolean. Follows the behavior of the HTML specification, in which the existence of the attribute indicates true regardless of the attribute's value. If the value is a boolean, it ignores the transformation. @param {*} value The value to convert to Boolean. @returns {Boolean} The corresponding boolean value.
